    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229860/extras/e5c54dfaad090133fb52c6e0df3c51ef.avif?t=1739660797\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229860/extras_big/e5c54dfaad090133fb52c6e0df3c51ef.avif?t=1739660797 width=800 height=806 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229860/extras/87a80a6e54400197fca0dd0d690b8209.avif?t=1739660797\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229860/extras_big/87a80a6e54400197fca0dd0d690b8209.avif?t=1739660797 width=800 height=244 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Last Spirit Origin is a fast-paced rogue-like adventure for up to four people. After you crash-land on your former home, now a chaotic alien world, you will face relentless machine enemies. Combine loot in surprising ways to enhance your abilities and master each character as you fight through hordes of frenzied robots. Use skillful combat and strategic planning to become the havoc you feared upon your first crash landing. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229860/extras/d40dfd0253940f02a0b9531a7a0f4511.avif?t=1739660797\" width=480 height=100 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229860/extras/7694baeb92c58e727366e6e7a1715adf.poster.avif?t=1739660797\" width=480 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229860/extras/7694baeb92c58e727366e6e7a1715adf.webm?t=1739660797\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229860/extra